  "detailed_description": "New Update:<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAdded Story Mode!!!<br />\r\n<br />\r\n17+ Game<br />\r\n<br />\r\nMinimum Players: 2<br />\r\n<br />\r\nMaximum Players: 10<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPlay at your own risk!!!!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nStrike of Horror is an online multiplayer horror game.<br />\r\nYou start by selecting a team of either being a ghost or a human.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nHuman Objective:<br />\r\nYou need to gather 3 sleeping potions to sleep through the horror, and while gathering make sure that the ghost doesn't catch you.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nGhost Objective:<br />\r\nYou need to capture as many humans as possible.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nNote: The teams will swap at the second round.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nEnjoy Scaring your friends.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nHints:<br />\r\n1) Try to capture your friends from behind to Jump Scare them.<br />\r\n2) Human is faster than ghost.",
  "about_the_game": "New Update:<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAdded Story Mode!!!<br />\r\n<br />\r\n17+ Game<br />\r\n<br />\r\nMinimum Players: 2<br />\r\n<br />\r\nMaximum Players: 10<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPlay at your own risk!!!!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nStrike of Horror is an online multiplayer horror game.<br />\r\nYou start by selecting a team of either being a ghost or a human.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nHuman Objective:<br />\r\nYou need to gather 3 sleeping potions to sleep through the horror, and while gathering make sure that the ghost doesn't catch you.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nGhost Objective:<br />\r\nYou need to capture as many humans as possible.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nNote: The teams will swap at the second round.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nEnjoy Scaring your friends.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nHints:<br />\r\n1) Try to capture your friends from behind to Jump Scare them.<br />\r\n2) Human is faster than ghost.",
